Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的行動全看我的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙應該沒辦法變成龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你無法見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才不是還陪我跳舞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.12,0:00:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把戴在左手的手鐲交來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不能一起跳舞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.50,0:00:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能 永遠不能了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等 跑太快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.76,0:00:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是紅龍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得死在這
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是純血龍族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.95,0:00:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說在遙遠的東方邊境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個與人類共存的龍族之鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:00:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說是個討好人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:01:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,膽小且毫無尊嚴的族群
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.09,0:01:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿薩謝爾他們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放馬過來 半吊子龍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要淘汰你那被人類砧汙的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽的血才不骯髒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾 趕緊離開那個惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人間太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦神聖之子在王都的消息走漏出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類必定會想方設法奪取你的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神聖之子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿薩謝爾 感謝你長久以來保護著艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我得把艾爾要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜…有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有加入部隊的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好 剩下的交給我們處理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還只是個孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜殺她的理由何在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 要是殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國王可不會坐視不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的國王興趣挺奇特的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像特別喜歡那個小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對國王來說 她這樣的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無異於玩完就扔的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都陪我跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還吻過我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你死之前 我就告訴你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍族姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令我殺了你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.45,0:07:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然肋骨斷了 不過還能堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是變生疏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 站得起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了硬上還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說為什麼貞德會來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著像是神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我想儘早離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是多餘的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能會輸給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向卑微的人類出賣靈魂的魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說得像你一個人解決了他一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不殺掉他們真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又冒出天真的念頭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 目前最重要的是先回基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想跟身為神的你談一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長話短說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要妨礙陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢說你們的所作所為是正義的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了明確這點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須阻止陛下的破壞行為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們的所作所為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充其量只是反賊的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們跟國王打算幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 凱撒 趕緊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們什麼都辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒 喂 真的不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在裡面不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失落成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是因為行動失敗和受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國王不死手鐲就取不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是我就打算幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果那傢伙跑來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜跟國王之間發生什麼事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德在這我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位天使又是從哪帶來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來這裡 一是為了將艾爾帶回天界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二是為了收拾叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想問你點事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:12:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利歐斯王在之前的戰爭中使用的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說 那種魔法技術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在於很遙遠的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即神和惡魔出現在這片大陸之前的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自太古時代起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:20.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等神明便封印了那種魔法技術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個破壞兵器就是用這技術製造出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百列大人是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪破壞力這麼驚人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是曾經統治這片大陸的前人們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的負面遺產之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等神明都無法弄清那東西的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只能封印起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利歐斯王不停襲擊神界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了弄到它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何陛下能駕馭那種技術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這一點 我們也無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想問的就這些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:03.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該跟我回神殿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾 你不願待在我身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量是為了履行責任而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 為了讓世界恢復和平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在必須戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是為此而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少自以為是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為此而生的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出生的理由只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老爸是為了你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才把你賜給她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這話有根據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要帶我來人間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我回神界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在那瞎編
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日後出什麼麻煩我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才不是胡說的呢 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以明天再回神界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想好好道別
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能 永遠不能了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命令我殺了你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺我是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 姆伽羅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回神界了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德會開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就跟姆伽羅一起在馬車睡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經成長了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.71,0:17:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽羅真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 走吧 姆伽羅真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢 你去幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去艾博斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到時候了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要解除狹縫的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.54,0:18:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻開始準備
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚 我把紅龍處理掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚的入侵者 好像到頭來沒抓到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不會還在王宮裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見亞歷山大沒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒看見 沒在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法陪你們一起戰鬥 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊就交給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你了 凱撒隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只是個越獄犯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也要一起回神界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…我就不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就算回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,運氣好的話被關起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會受到放逐出神界的判決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我未獲得加百列大人的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私自來到了人間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇？你都做了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我似乎多少能理解一點你的感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就留在人間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後跟他們一起摸清國王的真實意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別命令我 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一定會重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 絕對會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 姆伽羅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.62,0:20:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估計在阿薩謝爾那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽羅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請記住姆伽羅這個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 阿薩謝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.45,0:23:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱撒起得略微有點早
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,略微是多早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:23:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他獨自一人想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.61,0:23:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想什麼 說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.41,0:23:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神擊的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:23:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 吃肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
